name: Aspiring for Achievement Foundation (AAF
briefDescription: Aspiring for Achievement Foundation (AAF) was established by a group of youth with a dedication to promote empowerment of the marginalized.Current Programmes :Preschool center -Pre-primary education for better school entry of children  for3-5yrs children . Remedial centers and support classesAround 328 children coming to our centers   Community Health hygiene- Awareness Camps, Community Talks and Lectures Check-up camps for eye, dental, personal hygiene as well help needy patients for their medication cost. 2010- Women Health Camp, 127+ treated 2011-Children and Youth Medical Camp, 187 examined 2011- Eye Camp, 265 examined women and children (12 Adolescent Health Counseling Sessions in 2010 and 2011 236 attended)
